    "The existing studies identify the robustness of the k-NN algorithm with different k values for the GCN-based prediction tasks 47.",
    "We conducted experiments to assess the impact of the k-NN algorithm on GPA prediction.",
    "The results showed that the prediction performance remained consistent across different values of k (k = 1, 3, 5, 7, 10, 15) (Fig. 2a, b), indicating that GPA-GCN is relatively insensitive to the choice of k. The optimal value of k is selected as 5.",
    "Prediction comparison.",
